[[File:Firesu1.jpg|thumb|Fire Suppression Droid mark I]]
The '''fire suppression droid Mark I''' was similar in appearance to the [[KM1 mining droid]] and the [[KM1 mining droid|mining droid Mark I]], but its purpose was to put out fires using a [[carbonite gun]]. Such droids were used at the [[Peragus Mining Facility]]. The Exile, Meetra Surik encountered them on her travels shortly before the destruction of the [[Peragus Mining Facility]], when [[HK-50 series assassin droid|HK-50]] used these and various other mining droids to protect the Exile from the miners, who wished to give the Exile to the [[Exchange]]. Unfortunately, the [[Assassin droid/Legends|assassin droid]] underestimated the strength of a [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]], even an ex-Jedi who had severed her connection with [[The Force/Legends|the Force]]; as a result, the Exile awoke prematurely, and all of the facility's droids that had been commandeered turned on her.<ref name="Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords]]''</ref>

